gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pelicans 113, Suns 105
gameRecap.excerpt: CJ McCollum (31 points, seven 3PM, five assists) and Zion Williamson (29 points, 10 rebounds, seven assists) totaled 60 points as New Orleans defeated Phoenix, 113-105. Bradley Beal (33 points, seven 3PM, five assists) led Phoenix while Devin Booker (25 points, seven assists) and Kevin Durant (23 points, six assists) added 48 points.
